snippet.title: Gaelco Arcade 2 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured off the Original Evercade handheld. Here we have another six games from the Spanish arcade game maker, Gaelco (not to be confused with the Japanese developer, Jaleco)

Games in this cart:
00:07 - Big Karnak
04:00 - Maniac Square
09:24 - Squash
12:46 - TH Strikes Back: Thunder Hoop 2
18:53 - Touch and Go
22:42 - World Rally 2
